      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface reflects an exacting standard of care, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior. Mechanically superior and meticulously maintained, this unit offers a driving experience indistinguishable from new. This is an investment-grade opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
