      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s been my pride and joy and is honestly in showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found! It drives like a total dream and has been pampered in a heated garage since day one. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that looks and feels brand new, this is the one. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
