    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3, meticulously maintained to preserve its high-revving S54B32 powerplant. This unit features a fully addressed VANOS system with Beisan components and a proactively reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common chassis fatigue. The 3.2L atmospheric inline-six maintains factory-spec compression across all cylinders, breathing through individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential, with the suspension geometry preserved by fresh OEM bushings and Bilstein dampers. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior is free of the typical bolster wear or trim delamination. This is a mechanically synchronized, turn-key specimen for the serious driver.",
